title: january 11: earhart in oakland
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about one of Amelia Earhart’s flights from Hawaii to Oakland, and about her eventual mysterious disappearance. Then she talks about an epic Johnny Cash album. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
